title: Picnic Time's Regalio 813
transcripts: The Regalio by Picnic Time is and original design made of eco-friendly rubber wood. This three tiered combination serving tray and cheese board comes with three cheese tools and two swiveling serving surfaces. Two serving trays sit atop the cheeseboard base and swivel side to side creating the most fitting and attractive food arrangement. The rubber wood trays measure seven inches and eight inches and have a decorative groove along the edges to match the recess juice groove engraved on the ten inch cheeseboard base. The tiers are connected with two stainless steel poles and are topped off with a wooden finial. The tools are stainless steel with rubber wood handles and include a spreader with serrated edge, a hard cheese knife, and a fork tipped cheese knife. The Regalio makes a beautiful gift and a lovely centerpiece for any dinner party.
